allocate().details: Allocate unallocated funds on Vault to strategies.*

calculateSwapFeeIn().details: calculate the InSwap fee, i.e. fees for minting USDs

calculateSwapFeeOut().details: calculate the OutSwap fee, i.e. fees for redeeming USDs

returns._0: chiMint, i.e. chiTarget, since they share the same value

chiRedeem().details: calculate chiRedeem based on the formula at the end of section 2.2

chiTarget(uint256,uint256,uint256,uint25.details: calculate chiTarget by the formula in section 2.2 of the whitepaper

params.blockPassed: the number of blocks that have passed since USDs is launched, i.e. "Block Height"
params.precisionUSDs: the precision used in the variable "priceUSDs"
params.priceUSDs: the price of USDs, i.e. "USDs Price"

mintView(address,uint256,uint8).details: the general mintView function that display all related quantities based on mint types		valueType = 0: mintWithUSDs		valueType = 1: mintWithSPA		valueType = 2: mintWithColla		valueType = 3: mintWithETH

params.collaAddr: the address of user's chosen collateral
params.valueAmt: the amount of user input whose specific meaning depends on valueType
params.valueType: the type of user input whose interpretation is listed above in @dev

returns.SPABurnAmt: the amount of SPA to burn			collaDepAmt the amount of collateral to stake			USDsAmt the amount of USDs to mint			swapFeeAmount the amount of Inswapfee to pay

mintWithColla(address,uint256).details: mint USDs by entering collateral amount (excluding ETH)

params.CollaAmt: the amount of collateral to stake
params.collaAddr: the address of user's chosen collateral

mintWithCollaView(address,uint256).details: view related quantities for minting USDs with collateral amount to stake (excluding ETH)

params.CollaAmt: the amount of collateral to stake
params.collaAddr: the address of user's chosen collateral

returns.SPABurnAmt: the amount of SPA to burn			collaDepAmt the amount of collateral to stake			USDsAmt the amount of USDs to mint			swapFeeAmount the amount of Inswapfee to pay

mintWithEth().details: mint USDs by ETH note: this function needs changes when USDs is deployed on other blockchain platform

mintWithEthView(uint256).details: view related quantities for minting USDs with ETH

params.CollaAmt: the amount of ETH that the user stakes for minting USDs

returns.SPABurnAmt: the amount of SPA to burn			collaDepAmt the amount of collateral to stake			USDsAmt the amount of USDs to mint			swapFeeAmount the amount of Inswapfee to pay SPABurnAmt precision: 10^18 collaDepAmt precision: 10^collaAddrDecimal USDsAmt precision: 10^18 swapFeeAmount precision: swapFeePresion

mintWithSPA(address,uint256).details: mint USDs by entering SPA amount

params.SPAAmt: the amount of SPA to burn
params.collaAddr: the address of user's chosen collateral

mintWithSPAView(address,uint256).details: view related quantities for minting USDs with SPA amount to burn

params.SPAAmt: the amount of SPAs to burn
params.collaAddr: the address of user's chosen collateral

returns.SPABurnAmt: the amount of SPA to burn			collaDepAmt the amount of collateral to stake			USDsAmt the amount of USDs to mint			swapFeeAmount the amount of Inswapfee to pay

mintWithUSDs(address,uint256).details: mint USDs by entering USDs amount

params.USDsMintAmt: the amount of USDs to be minted
params.collaAddr: the address of user's chosen collateral

mintWithUSDsView(address,uint256).details: view related quantities for minting USDs with USDs amount

params.USDsMintAmt: the amount of USDs to mint
params.collaAddr: the address of user's chosen collateral

returns.SPABurnAmt: the amount of SPA to burn			collaDepAmt the amount of collateral to stake			USDsAmt the amount of USDs to mint			swapFeeAmount the amount of Inswapfee to pay

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

rebase().details: Calculate the total value of assets held by the Vault and all      strategies and update the supply of USDs.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._asset: the address of the new supported collateral

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

updateSwapInFee(bool).details: disable swapInFee, i.e. mint becomes free

updateSwapOutFee(bool).details: disable swapOutFee, i.e. redeem becomes free
